node.text: You guys have been asking me for so long now and I’ve had to keep this secret 🤐 but i can finally say, THE GUYS AND I ARE BACK! Season 3 of @carmastersrusttoriches on @netflix airs August 4th! Make sure you guys tag Netflix and let them know how excited you are, and click the link in my bio to leave comments on the official trailer too 🏁 #carmastersrusttoriches #constancenunes

node.text:
You guys are always asking me for tips and pointers and how-tos…to be honest most of the time I’m so busy working I just forget to stop and take photos or videos and I’m the only person at #carsbyconstance so I literally have to beg friends to come by to help me film stuff or take my photo 😂 🙈 But I’m going to try and get you guys just little things I come across during the day that might be helpful to some of you… 

Today I have a little mustang with an equally little transmission leak 😅…obviously there can be other culprits leading to transmission leaks, but in this case it happened to be this one. Who here has had this issue before? 🏁 #constancenunes #carsbyconstance

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Constance Nunes on August 10, 2021 tagging @bendpak. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
It’s been such an undertaking working on my clients cars while simultaneously moving into my new shop. I’m so grateful for everyone who has believed in me and that my brand partners like @bendpak have always been super supportive of my goals. Getting my new lift in was such a lifesaver and couldn’t be more grateful 🙏🏼 (or ready to start using it 😬) #carsbyconstance #constancenunes 

*btw, the comeback kid to my left is #ripdog and the lady in red is a girl I like to call #msbrandy …you will see why further into the build 😉

node.text:
Had the most amazing time @nhra thanks to @shoeracing 🏁I got to bring my dad down to the starting line, meet with all the amazing team drivers, and of course get to see some badass race cars 🤘🏽 Can’t wait for more events later in the season…good luck out there today to the whole team! #carsbyconstance #constancenunes 

(Wearing @guess @marciano 🖤)

node.text: You guys have been asking me for so long now and I’ve had to keep this secret 🤐 but i can finally say, THE GUYS AND I ARE BACK! Season 3 of @carmastersrusttoriches on @netflix airs August 4th! Make sure you guys tag Netflix and let them know how excited you are, and click the link in my bio to leave comments on the official trailer too 🏁 #carmastersrusttoriches #constancenunes
